      • getMatching

        public List<String> getMatching(String library,
                                String iconName,
                                String dimensions)
        Returns the paths to matching icon resources given name, dimensions, and library name, any one of which may contain wildcard characters.
        Parameters:
        library - Library name containing the icon (e.g., "silk"). If null, all libraries are searched.
        iconName - Name of the requested icon (e.g., "help*.png").
        dimensions - Dimensions of the requested icon (e.g., "16x*").
        Returns:
        The icon path.
